      <title>合氣道進步的秘訣【第0234回】　君啊，切莫焦躁</title>
      <link>https://kaku-budo.github.io/blog/aikido/tips/part-0201-0300/t-0234-stay-with-one/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 11 Jan 2026 19:29:00 +0800</pubDate>
